<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:09:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>纳莱迪人真的埋葬了死者吗？现在有办法可以查到</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/did-homo-naledi-really-bury-its-dead-now-there-are-ways-to-find-out/0000018c-2080-d9ef-abcd-3ea10b130000</link><description>一篇新论文提出了利用地球科学技术来减少考古发现的不确定性的案例，例如是否有小脑人类在墙壁上雕刻并埋葬了死者</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/did-homo-naledi-really-bury-its-dead-now-there-are-ways-to-find-out/0000018c-2080-d9ef-abcd-3ea10b130000</guid></item><item><title>闭嘴跳舞：特拉维夫的俱乐部场景因不关心政治而付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/our-parties-contributed-to-the-deafening-whitewashing-of-the-state-of-israel/0000018c-15a0-dd03-a7ff-bfb85afb0000</link><description>自 2002 年“狂欢反对占领”以来，以色列的夜生活场景和政治活动之间就没有任何联系。现在我们在世界舞台上为此付出了沉重的代价</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 15:49:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/our-parties-contributed-to-the-deafening-whitewashing-of-the-state-of-israel/0000018c-15a0-dd03-a7ff-bfb85afb0000</guid></item><item><title>新研究揭穿了来自埃巴勒山的有争议的圣经“诅咒碑”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-30/ty-article/new-studies-debunk-controversial-biblical-curse-tablet-from-mt-ebal/0000018c-20b6-d21c-abae-76bee75f0000</link><description>在约旦河西岸的“约书亚祭坛”发现的一块铅碑被吹捧为最古老的希伯来铭文。怀疑论者怀疑它什么也没说，而是一个钓鱼重量</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 15:37:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-30/ty-article/new-studies-debunk-controversial-biblical-curse-tablet-from-mt-ebal/0000018c-20b6-d21c-abae-76bee75f0000</guid></item><item><title>谁来统治加沙？谁来重建它？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/who-will-govern-gaza-who-will-rebuild-it/0000018c-2093-d9ef-abcd-3eb3726b0000</link><description>战后第二天，将出现安全、治理以及谁将为加沙真正大规模重建买单的根本问题 — — 这些努力对于防止导致 10 月 7 日的激进化至关重要</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 15:15:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/who-will-govern-gaza-who-will-rebuild-it/0000018c-2093-d9ef-abcd-3eb3726b0000</guid></item><item><title>与哈马斯作战的受伤人员：“身体上有所进步，但情感上的挑战变得更加困难”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/wounded-battling-hamas-you-progress-physically-but-the-emotional-challenge-gets-harder/0000018c-2038-d9ef-abcd-3e393e430000</link><description>特拉维夫附近一家医院的康复中心里挤满了 10 月 7 日拯救生命的以色列士兵。现在，他们决心康复，以纪念那些未能幸存的朋友</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 14:29:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/wounded-battling-hamas-you-progress-physically-but-the-emotional-challenge-gets-harder/0000018c-2038-d9ef-abcd-3e393e430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列必须澄清：不驱逐加沙人。加沙没有以色列定居点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-clarify-no-expulsion-of-gazans-no-israeli-settlements-in-gaza/0000018c-2043-dc03-a9ec-3c7b97600000</link><description>我们，一群以色列哲学家，捍卫以色列免受战争罪指控。但我们震惊地听到内塔尼亚胡政府中要求使加沙人永久流离失所的险恶声音：这将是反人类罪</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 14:22:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-clarify-no-expulsion-of-gazans-no-israeli-settlements-in-gaza/0000018c-2043-dc03-a9ec-3c7b97600000</guid></item><item><title>不是两个国家，不是一个国家：以色列人和巴勒斯坦人摆脱灾难的新出路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/not-two-states-not-one-state-a-new-way-out-of-disaster-for-israelis-and-palestinians/0000018c-1fc0-d21c-abae-7ffc7f960000</link><description>只要看看加沙就知道以色列和巴勒斯坦的艰难分离会带来什么。坚固的围栏、地下屏障——如果更多的开放和更少的隔离是更好的答案呢？听起来很疯狂，但有一个逻辑</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 14:20:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/not-two-states-not-one-state-a-new-way-out-of-disaster-for-israelis-and-palestinians/0000018c-1fc0-d21c-abae-7ffc7f960000</guid></item><item><title>一名拉比法庭法官、一名校长和一名怀孕教师：耶路撒冷恐怖袭击的以色列受害者身份已确定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/israeli-victims-of-hamas-jerusalem-terror-attack-identified/0000018c-2032-d9ef-abcd-3e3352170000</link><description>周四上午耶路撒冷枪击事件的三名受害者被确认为 73 岁的拉比 Elimelech Wasserman、67 岁的 Hanna Ifergan 和 24 岁的 Liviya Dickman</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 13:54:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/israeli-victims-of-hamas-jerusalem-terror-attack-identified/0000018c-2032-d9ef-abcd-3e3352170000</guid></item><item><title>伦敦议会取消烛台安装，担心加沙战争“加剧紧张局势”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/london-council-calls-off-menorah-instillation-fearing-inflaming-tensions-amid-gaza-war/0000018c-1fb7-d9ef-abcd-1fb734aa0000</link><description>在一封泄露的电子邮件中，官员们表示，临时安装比每年在整个假期期间展示巨型烛台更合适。自持续冲突开始以来，英国的反犹太主义事件急剧增加</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 13:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/london-council-calls-off-menorah-instillation-fearing-inflaming-tensions-amid-gaza-war/0000018c-1fb7-d9ef-abcd-1fb734aa0000</guid></item><item><title>随着哈马斯人质协议的落实，以色列考虑允许释放人质的选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/as-hamas-hostage-deal-materializes-israel-considers-options-to-also-allow-mens-release/0000018c-202b-da36-a1de-672ff0e30000</link><description>周四的人质释放预计将把最后一批以色列妇女和儿童从加沙地带带回以色列。一位熟悉谈判的消息人士表示，“每个人都清楚，现在恢复战斗将大大减少在不久的将来达成进一步协议的机会”</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 13:14:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/as-hamas-hostage-deal-materializes-israel-considers-options-to-also-allow-mens-release/0000018c-202b-da36-a1de-672ff0e30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-加沙战争进入新阶段：拯救大兵内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/how-do-you-gaslight-an-entire-nation-ask-netanyahu/0000018c-1f93-db78-adcc-bfffdcbf0000</link><description>不出所料，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡将竭尽全力避免为以色列历史上最严重的灾难承担责任，甚至对 10 月 7 日及其后果提出全新的叙述</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 12:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/how-do-you-gaslight-an-entire-nation-ask-netanyahu/0000018c-1f93-db78-adcc-bfffdcbf0000</guid></item><item><title>针对以色列的秘密学术抵制：“美国机构不会有以色列研究人员”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/covert-academic-boycott-against-israel-u-s-institutions-wont-have-israeli-researchers/0000018c-1c07-d9ef-abcd-1e274e0f0000</link><description>当地教授表示，自针对哈马斯的战争开始以来，西方校园的反以色列情绪正在减缓与以色列研究人员的合作：“拒绝审查出版物，拒绝参加以色列的会议，并终止邀请”去国外参加会议&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 12:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/covert-academic-boycott-against-israel-u-s-institutions-wont-have-israeli-researchers/0000018c-1c07-d9ef-abcd-1e274e0f0000</guid></item><item><title>亲巴勒斯坦抗议者在墨尔本酒店大堂骚扰加沙人质的以色列家庭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-30/ty-article/pro-palestine-protesters-harass-family-of-gaza-hostages-in-melbourne-hotel-lobby/0000018c-1fc0-d9ef-abcd-1fe104ab0000</link><description>澳大利亚总理表示，“我对这些抗议者的行为感到震惊，并谴责他们。”自加沙战争开始以来，澳大利亚对以色列人和犹太人的敌意不断增加</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 11:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-30/ty-article/pro-palestine-protesters-harass-family-of-gaza-hostages-in-melbourne-hotel-lobby/0000018c-1fc0-d9ef-abcd-1fe104ab0000</guid></item><item><title>身患绝症的以色列母亲呼吁拜登帮助释放被哈马斯囚禁的女儿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/terminally-ill-israeli-mom-calls-on-biden-to-help-release-daughter-from-hamas-captivity/0000018c-1f8d-db78-adcc-bffd3a820000</link><description>一段广为流传的诺瓦狂欢节袭击事件视频显示，人质诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani) 被哈马斯恐怖分子抓获并骑摩托车带走。她的母亲在视频中告诉她，“请知道，我们已尽一切努力让你获释”</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 10:22:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/terminally-ill-israeli-mom-calls-on-biden-to-help-release-daughter-from-hamas-captivity/0000018c-1f8d-db78-adcc-bffd3a820000</guid></item><item><title>一个贝都因家庭请求以色列不要忘记他们在加沙被扣为人质的亲戚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/a-bedouin-family-is-asking-israel-to-not-forget-about-their-relatives-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018c-1f82-dc03-a9ec-1ffb98860000</link><description>10 月 7 日，贝都因家庭的四名成员在基布兹霍利特工作时被绑架。作为延长停火协议的一部分，家人希望 17 岁的艾莎和 18 岁的比拉尔能够在周四获释</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 10:06:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/a-bedouin-family-is-asking-israel-to-not-forget-about-their-relatives-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018c-1f82-dc03-a9ec-1ffb98860000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷恐怖袭击造成三名以色列人死亡、六人受伤；哈马斯宣称对此事负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/three-israelis-killed-in-jerusalem-attack-hamas-affiliated-assailants-shot-dead/0000018c-1f4a-da36-a1de-5f6fc5200000</link><description>枪击事件发生在耶路撒冷正门一个繁忙的公交车站。恐怖分子来自东耶路撒冷，其中一名此前曾在以色列被监禁</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 09:20:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/three-israelis-killed-in-jerusalem-attack-hamas-affiliated-assailants-shot-dead/0000018c-1f4a-da36-a1de-5f6fc5200000</guid></item><item><title>美国首位犹太裔国务卿、颇具争议的外交偶像亨利·基辛格去世，享年 100 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/henry-kissinger-first-u-s-jewish-secretary-of-state-and-contentious-icon-dies-at-100/0000018c-1ef0-db78-adcc-befc49f70000</link><description>基辛格是一名十几岁时与家人一起逃离纳粹德国的犹太人，在理查德·尼克松和杰拉尔德·福特总统领导下对全球事务产生了非凡的影响，既赢得了诽谤，也获得了诺贝尔和平奖</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 06:47:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/henry-kissinger-first-u-s-jewish-secretary-of-state-and-contentious-icon-dies-at-100/0000018c-1ef0-db78-adcc-befc49f70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的停火又迎来了战争的关键时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/as-the-truce-with-hamas-progresses-decision-time-for-israel-approaches/0000018c-1ce6-da36-a1de-5fe797c20000</link><description>至此，以色列既可以继续战斗，又可以进一步释放更多人质的幻想可能会破灭。由于哈马斯向以色列索要的价格，需要达成另一项协议，而且实现起来会更加困难</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 04:04:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/as-the-truce-with-hamas-progresses-decision-time-for-israel-approaches/0000018c-1ce6-da36-a1de-5fe797c20000</guid></item><item><title>“人道主义外交”现在将为以色列和哈马斯引领道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/humanitarian-diplomacy-will-now-lead-the-way-for-israel-and-hamas/0000018c-1d03-dc03-a9ec-1d7b00b00000</link><description>人道主义援助已成为这场运动的一个组成部分，这要归功于它以释放人质的形式为以色列做出的贡献，以及通过它至少可以实现战争目标的希望</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 04:03:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/humanitarian-diplomacy-will-now-lead-the-way-for-israel-and-hamas/0000018c-1d03-dc03-a9ec-1d7b00b00000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列人从哈马斯的囚禁中获释，另外八人即将获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-live/12-israelis-four-thai-nationals-released-from-hamas-captivity-in-gaza/0000018c-1e28-db78-adcc-be7c50fb0007</link><description>耶路撒冷枪击事件造成三人死亡、六人受伤 ■ 卡塔尔：以色列与哈马斯停火将于周四继续 ■ 以色列收到将于周四释放的人质名单 ■ 周三从哈马斯囚禁中获释的 16 名人质：12 名以色列人和 4 名泰国国民 ■美国国务卿布林肯抵达以色列 ■ 自10月7日以来，以色列至少有1,200名平民和士兵丧生；加沙仍有超过 159 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：加沙至少有 14,000 人死亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 03:55:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-live/12-israelis-four-thai-nationals-released-from-hamas-captivity-in-gaza/0000018c-1e28-db78-adcc-be7c50fb0007</guid></item></channel></rss>